      <note>This job is intended to, based on the following variables, gather the appropriate error information in 
the defined response file format and place it in an outbound directory to be moved to the SFTP server.  
This movement to the outbound SFTP server may become part of this process in the future.

Required variables:

-V_icn : document interchange control number (a.k.a. source_document_control_number)
-V_schema_name : Redshift schema containing error information tables (errors_and_rejects_details 
and errors_and_rejects_headers tables)
-short_filename : this job will create a response file with the name ${short_filename}_response.csv
-V_pentaho_folder_name : This job will place the response file in the following directory: 
/pentaho-workspace/data/${V_pentaho_folder_name}/outbound</note>
